title Corpo app

actor User
User->Core: Get list of event
Core->Database: Retrieve list of available events for user
Database-->User: Http 200 - List of events
User->Core: Subscribe to event
Core->+Database: Store user to event
Database->Notification core: send email with summary of registration
Database-->-User: Http 204 - No content 


note over Notification core: 1 day before the event
Notification core->Notification core: Send a reminder to user
